text:
hey, all. i’m building out a template with the HubSpot video module and wanted to add some default content to it. i’m using the following markup in my template:

```{% dnd_module
	path="@HubSpot/video",
	embed_field={
		"oembed_url": "<https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ScMzIvxBSi4>",
		"size_type": "auto_full_width"
	}
%}```
in preview and when i spin up a new page using that template, the video is not displaying until i go into the module and make a change to the video url, for example, replacing the oembed_url value.

what am i missing?
Looks like the oembed_response value is needed.
